subproject.description: The CHSED JP is built upon five achievable outcomes and based on national, sub-national and sectoral priorities for culture and development. Interventions include the provision of policy support, improvement of capacities in the field of the protection, promotion and management of cultural assets, safeguarding of the most valuable cultural heritage monuments and sites, and strengthening the cultural industries sector for socio-economic development and achievement of the MDGs.
subproject.gender code: Gender equality as a significant objective
